      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Lihds ar teem Sleekſneem\nnn ſchaureem Lohgeem nn Mar-\ngahn wiſſapkahrt trejâs Rin-\ndês/ tam Sleekſnim pretti bija\nApklahjamée no Kohka wiſſap-\nkahrt/ un no tahs Semmes lihds\nteem Lohgeem/ un tee paſchi Loh-\ngt bija apſeati.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiſſch (arri mehroja)\nto/ kas wirs tahm Durwim bi-\nja/ prohti lihds tam eekſchejam\nnn abrejam Nammmam/ un pee\nwiſſas Scenas wiſſapkahrt/ tik\nlabbi ahra ka Eekſchpuﬀê.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas bija darrihts ar\nKerubim un Palma-Kohkeem /\nta ka weenis Palma-Kohks bija\nstarp Kerubu un Kerubu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ikweenam Kerubam\nbija diwi Waigi/ weens Zilweka\nWaigê prett to Palma-Kohku\nno ſchihs Puﬀes/ un weens Lau-\nwas Waigs prett to Palma-\nKohku no winnas Puﬀes/ ta\ntas bija wiſſa Namina wiſſap-\nkahrt taiſihts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "No tahs Semmes lihds\nto Durwju Wtrß-Gallain bija\ntee Kerubim darriti/ ir pee ta\nDeewa Namna Scenas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta Deewa Namina\nStendeki bija tſchetrahin Kan-\ntim/ un tahs fwehtas Weetas\nTaiſſjums ieraudſijabs tapatt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Das Augſtums ta Kohka\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Altara vija frihs Ohlekſchu\nwinna Garrums diwi O\nſchu/ un winnam bijfawi S\nri/ un winna Garrums un ri\nna Seenas bija no Kohka.\nwiſſch ruunaja us nan: S\nirr tas Galds/ kas preeſſch\nRUNGA buhs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un taim Deewa Na-\nnam/ un tai fwehtai Weeta\nja ifkatran diwi Durwis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un pee tahm Dur-\nbija diwi Spahrni/ ko wa-\natwehrt un aiſwehrt / divi-\nweenahm Durwim / un i\nSpahrni pee ohtrahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un pee tahm/ prohti-\ntahm Deewa Namna Dur-\nbija Kerubim un Palma-\ndarriti / itt ka pee tahm\nnahm darriti bija/ un us\nPreeſſch Namina Preeſſch-\nAbravuffes bija reſnis Bal-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un pee teem febau-\nLohgeem bija arridsan Pal-\nKohki no ſchihs un no wi-\nPuﬀes fahnis to Preeſſch-\nnu/ un pee ta Namna Sa-\nKambareem / un pee teem\nneem Balkeem.\n"
    }
  ],
